posts.post_title: FS: 1917 Zeenut Sleepy Bill Burns 1919 Black Sox Gambler SGC Graded SOLD
posts.post_content:
This is a pretty tough card with a total graded population of 3 between PSA & SGC. This one displays nicely, and of course we know Sleepy Bill Burns from the 1919 Black Sox Scandal.  Cool writing on the back. Price is SOLD delivered PayPal Friends/Family please. Thanks for looking.

Joe K
